    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant with its factory-spec 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This example exhibits exceptional mechanical provenance, with the critical VANOS system overhauled and the rear subframe reinforced for structural longevity. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a perfectly calibrated limited-slip differential. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the factory finish retains its deep luster with no evidence of panel misalignment. Every bushing is tight, and the suspension geometry remains true to OEM specifications, offering the purist driving dynamics this chassis is renowned for. A turn-key investment for the discerning collector.",
