    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle is a verified time capsule, meticulously maintained in showroom condition. The exterior boasts a mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks, scratches, or stone chips, further protected by a high-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery shows no bolster wear, the carpets are pristine under factory mats, and it has never been smoked in. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the heated seats, operates with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive binder of every service record since its first mile. Always stored in a climate-controlled garage and never driven in inclement weather, this car represents a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning driver to own a flawless example of the model.",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
