    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This car is an absolute gem\u2014I\u2019ve honestly babied it since day one! It's in pristine condition, inside and out, with that 'new car' smell still lingering. No scratches, no dents, just pure driving bliss. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 44500.0,
