    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the zenith of naturally aspirated engineering. The S54 inline-six remains the centerpiece, featuring high-pressure double-VANOS and six individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response and a screaming 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen has been meticulously curated; the critical rod bearing service is complete, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to mitigate common chassis fatigue. Power is channeled through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring peerless corner-exit traction. The suspension geometry is preserved to factory specifications, with all bushings and dampers providing the communicative feedback these cars are legendary for. This is a turn-key, collector-grade example for the discerning enthusiast who values mechanical integrity.",
